act_info_by_cus = act_info %>%
  group_by(cus_id) %>%
  summarize(n=n())
## `summarise()` ungrouping output (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(act_info_by_cus, aes(n)) + geom_histogram() #  1~2

3.3 trd_kr

trd_kr = trd_kr %>%
  mutate(orr_dt=ymd(orr_dt))

ggplot(trd_kr, aes(orr_rtn_hur)) + geom_bar(stat='count') # 9  

ggplot(trd_kr, aes(lst_cns_hur)) + geom_bar(stat='count') #   

ggplot(trd_kr, aes(sby_dit_cd)) + geom_bar(stat='count') #    2

ggplot(trd_kr, aes(orr_mdi_dit_cd)) + geom_bar(stat='count') #  MTS

ggplot(trd_kr, aes(orr_pr)) + geom_histogram() + scale_x_log10()
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

trd_kr_by_act = trd_kr %>%
  group_by(act_id) %>%
  summarize(orr_cnt=n())
## `summarise()` ungrouping output (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(trd_kr_by_act, aes(orr_cnt)) + geom_histogram() #  100 
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

trd_kr_by_dt = trd_kr %>%
  group_by(orr_dt) %>%
  summarize(orr_cnt=n())
## `summarise()` ungrouping output (override with `.groups` argument)
ggplot(trd_kr_by_dt, aes(x=orr_dt, y=orr_cnt)) + geom_line() # 19 1 ~ 20 6 , 20    

trd_kr_merged = merge(x=trd_kr, y=act_info, by='act_id', all.x=TRUE)
trd_kr_merged = merge(x=trd_kr_merged, y=cus_info, by='cus_id', all.x=TRUE)

ggplot(trd_kr_merged, aes(cus_age)) + geom_bar(stat='count')
